Ousmane Zeidine Ahmeye (amụrụ ya na 9 June 1994), bụ onye Nijeria na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba bọọlụ dị ka onye na-aga n'ihu.
Na June 2013, Ahmeye bịnyere aka na otu na agba bọọlụ na France Angers. N'abalị iri na asaa n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 2016, Ahmeye bịnyere aka n'akwụkwọ maka otu egwuregwu Kyrgyzstan League Dordoi Bishkek.
Ahmeye mere nke mbụ ya maka ndị otu egwuregwu mba Niger megide Burkina Faso na 23 Machị 2013.
Ndekọ ọnụ ọgụgụ ziri ezi dị ka egwuregwu a gbara na 23 Machị 2013
